3.选4个电机
4.选一个骨架

2025.4.2- Now 12:00 PM (English)
Today I started this project on drones. My first idea was to have the drones fly in first, and then iterate and update them step by step.
Current idea:
1. Choose a CPU as the controller
2. Choose a Bluetooth (try to add SM card as much as possible)
3. Select 4 motors
4. Choose a skeleton
